title: XM music: Outron - Age is Just a Hexadecimal (GUS PnP clone)
description:
"Age is Just a Hexadecimal" by Outron, 5th at Assembly Summer 2022. Art "Enter the Abyss" by FadeOne/Abyss, 2nd at Revision 2019.

VOGONS ARGUS project thread:
https://www.vogons.org/viewtopic.php?f=62&t=42431

- Retro PC circa 2002. MS-DOS 7.1 (Win98SE), Athlon XP 2200+ etc.
- Player: XTC-Play 0.97c
- Soundcard: AMD InterWave (GUS PnP clone made by David E. Larsson, based on the ARGUS project)
- Mixer: 44100Hz, 16bits, stereo, interpolation (own processor)
